reviewText: Although this was rated a one (1) star movie, I really enjoyed it!!

DO NOT BUY THIS DVD!!! This movie is a hijacked street version of a film called "Crazy Like a Fox". A thief took off original credits and opening titles, replaced all the names and repackaged this DVD as his own. Besides, it's all washed out and the audio is out sync. He managed to sell all over the place, including Walmart. The original film is going to be released soon. It is directed by Tony Abulu and his website is [...]/. NOTE TO [...]: This is a sad, painful and blatant copyright violation. You should not be participating in the sales of this DVD!!!
